<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />Why are you bowed down, my soul?</para>

<para style="q1">Why are you upset within me?</para>

<para style="q1">Hope in God, for again I will praise him who is my salvation.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />My God, my soul is bowed down within me,</para>

<para style="q1">therefore I call you to mind from the land of the Jordan,</para>

<para style="q1">from the three peaks of Mount Hermon, and from the hill of Mizar.</para>
